title: Terrific 2 Bed, 2 Bath in Round Rock
posting_body: ['LIVE A LIFE OF TRUE LUXURY', 'If you’ve been searching for a living experience that combines urban sophistication with suburban convenience, look no further!', 'This brand new resort-style apartment community is the latest Round Rock turn on.', 'This stylish apartment home features craftsman finishes, modern features, and an open, airy layout.', 'Embark on culinary adventures in your gourmet kitchen, with stainless steel appliances,  quartz countertops, subway tile backsplashes, and an island for extra prep space.', 'Spa-inspired bathrooms feature a seamless glass enclosed shower & a relaxing soaking tub.', 'Unpack gleefully into your oversized closets.', 'Additional included special features are a built-in work station and full sized washer and dryer.', 'Outdoor recreation areas include a resort-style swimming pool with cabanas, courtyard kitchen and dining areas, gaming, open-air TV lounge, and a yoga and fitness lawn area.', 'Reach for your lap top & head to fully connected co-working headquarters with shared and private office spaces.', 'Sandwich in a great workout between work & play in the cutting-edge 24-hour athletic club with interactive workouts, spin bikes, and more.', 'This pet friendly community will be adored by your furry friends with the expansive dog park and SPAW, built just for them.', 'It’s time to live the lifestyle you deserve.', 'This Locator gives loyalty rebates of $50-$250.00!', 'Ask me how to get yours!', ' :)', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'ID:  32', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
